name: Eden Development
tag_list: web, web2-0, ajax, web-development, agency, consultancy, software, blog
overview:
Eden Development is a software development consultancy based in Winchester, UK, providing development services to businesses in the UK, Europe and USA.

Founded in 2004, Eden has steadily grown to become a medium sized and well known software consultancy employing 9 people in their Winchester office. The company incorporates a number of agile techniques, including iterative development and pair programming, and regularly cites the importance of build quality and a deep understanding of client objectives.

The company has an active blog commentating on technical and business issues facing developers.
